title: The suspect in a Texas mass shooting vanishes, and authorities have 'zero leads,' FBI says
description: A man suspected of using an AR-15 rifle to kill five neighbors execution-style continued to elude an army of law enforcement hunting for him outside Houston over the weekend.

title: Tornado flips cars, damages homes in coastal Florida city
description: A touched down in Palm Beach Gardens, Florida, on Saturday as a powerful storm system brought intense rain and powerful winds to the state, overturning cars, damaging homes and snapping tree branches.

title: College baseball player shot by stray bullet during game, police say
description: A stray bullet struck a college baseball player for Texas A&M-Texarkana in the middle of a game Saturday, according to local police and the university.

title: RNC Chair Ronna McDaniel: 2024 GOP candidates must tackle abortion 'head on'
description: RNC Chair Ronna McDaniel said Sunday that many Republican candidates refused to talk about the issue during the 2022 midterm election cycle.

title: DHS Secretary Mayorkas calls for congressional support ahead of expected migrant surge
description: Homeland Security Sec. Alejandro Mayorkas said Sunday that he is focused on getting congressional support to fix the "broken immigration system" in the U.S.

title: Backlash against AI supermodels triggers wider fears in fashion workforce
description: Plans by Levi’s to test out virtual clothing models have collided with longer-running concerns around diversity and labor protections in the industry.

title: Armed U.S. drones escort evacuation of American citizens in war-torn Sudan
description: Armed drones flew above a convoy of buses evacuating several hundred American citizens through war torn Sudan, a U.S. official familiar with the matter confirmed to NBC News.

title: This Supreme Court is slow to issue rulings — glacially slow
description: The Supreme Court has decided fewer cases at this point of the term than at any time in the last 100 years.

title: Ticketmaster says ‘Verified Fan’ registration doesn’t measure fandom. Some fans think it should.
description: Ticketmaster doesn’t account for dedication when it selects buyers to participate in its Verified Fan system. Some fans want that to change.
